Package io.smint.clapi.consumer.integration.core.contracts

Interface ISmintIoMetadataElement

All Known Implementing Classes:
SmintIoMetadataElementImpl
public interface ISmintIoMetadataElement
Element of meta data used with Smint.io assets.

Each meta data element is a structured element, containing various properties. In effect it is like a JSON object with a lot of properties (getValues()), saved to the storage with the key getKey().

In order to speed up synchronization, provide a secure mapping and ease the work load on the sync target DAM abstraction layer ISyncTarget, the meta data items are cached within the synchronization job. So instances are probably long living.

    • getTargetMetadataUuid

      String getTargetMetadataUuid()
      Provides the ID, this meta data element uses on the sync target side.

      This value provides a 1:1 mapping from the Smint.io API key (getKey()) to the key on the sync target side. This is the value that is used when settings meta data to BaseSyncAssets

      Returns:
      the ID used on the sync target side.
